articles.author: Associated Press
articles.title: Protesters line highway in Florida Everglades to oppose ‘Alligator Alcatraz’ - CNN
articles.description: A coalition of groups, ranging from environmental activists to Native Americans advocating for their ancestral homelands, converged outside an airstrip in the Florida Everglades Saturday to protest the imminent construction of an immigrant detention center.
